---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const page_title = "About Us";
const page_description = "Discover the project behind privacy-crypto.com and our educational mission to spread awareness about financial privacy.";
---

<Layout title={page_title} description={page_description} maxWidth="max-w-4xl" lang="en">
  <header class="mb-8 border-b border-white/[0.05] pb-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-white">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">{page_description}</p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
    <div class="bento-card p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border border-[#0066FF]/20 bg-[#0066FF]/5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0066FF]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            Our Educational Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong>privacy-crypto.com</strong> was created as a purely informational and educational hub for privacy-conscious crypto users worldwide. Our goal is to collect and catalog the tools, best practices, and resources related to digital privacy and the responsible use of cryptocurrencies.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            In an increasingly complex web3 landscape, often plagued by scams, we believe it is essential to have a clear point of reference that explains how to maintain sovereignty over your data and your finances.
        </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">What We Do NOT Do</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-400 mb-8 list-none pl-0">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
            <span><strong>No Financial Advice:</strong> We do not provide trading signals, we do not recommend investments, and we do not promise returns. All information is strictly educational.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
            <span><strong>No Fundraising:</strong> We will never accept deposits, we will never ask for your private keys, and we will never manage funds on behalf of third parties. If someone contacts you in our name asking for funds, it is a scam.</span>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Independence and Security</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We select and review tools (such as self-custody wallets, exchanges, and VPNs) based on security criteria, an open-source approach, and respect for user privacy. Our content is designed to help you conduct <em>your own</em> research in a more informed and secure way (DYOR - Do Your Own Research).
    </p>

  </div>
</Layout>
